ttern for network filter configuration\n\n## Key Files Summary\n\nThe bypass and passthrough logic spans these C++ files:\n- **HTTP Filter Core**: ext_authz.h, ext_authz.cc (per-route bypass at line 403-405, skip_check flag)\n- **HTTP Configuration**: config.h, config.cc (route-specific config factory)\n- **Network Filter**: ext_authz.h, ext_authz.cc in network/ext_authz/ (similar bypass logic)\n- **Common Base**: ext_authz.h (Response and CheckStatus definitions)\n- **Response Processing**: ext_authz_grpc_impl.h/cc, ext_authz_http_impl.h (converts authorization responses)\n- **Request Building**: check_request_utils.h/cc (creates CheckRequest from HTTP/network streams)"
